## Description {#details}

This file implements a map that provides insertion order iteration.

The interface is purposefully minimal. The key is assumed to be cheap to copy and 2 copies are kept, one for indexing in a DenseMap, one for iteration in a SmallVector.

<Link id="l00188" /><CodeLine lineNumber="188"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// Returns an iterator to the element following the one which was removed,</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00190" /><CodeLine lineNumber="190"><Highlight kind="comment">  ///</Highlight></CodeLine>
